# Policy-first cascade

Changes in `lib/policy` drive the platform. After edits:

1. `pnpm vertical:check` (if vertical/onboarding/presets)
2. `pnpm vertical:doc-check` (if vertical docs/registry)
3. `pnpm codegen` if API contract changed
4. `pnpm run typecheck`
5. Verify `artifacts/*` consumers — no duplicated vertical lists or hardcoded salon UI

Skill: `.cursor/skills/livia-vertical-change`

Do not hand-edit `lib/api-zod` or `lib/api-client-react`.
